  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduo a NASM</title>

    <para>
      <application>NASM</application> (Netwide Assembler) is an 80x86 assembler
designed for portability and modularity. It includes a disassembler as well.
    </para>

    &lfs113_checked;

